{"tid":265932,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【旅伴】有無巴絲六月十號會係台灣","createTime":"2017-06-01T05:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T13:56:19.000Z","uid":40003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4de95a39d2656a829087c61dd0c47360080efce0","tid":265932,"uid":40003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:21:29.000Z","msg":"上兩次去台灣都係去台北<br />\n今次見之前hk express mega sales 有平飛買左六月十飛台中，十四號由台北翻香港<br />\n一個人飛，<br />\n有無巴絲有興趣一齊食個飯或者去下景點之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住宿都未訂<br />\n初步有構思想去高美濕地或者青境養場玩兩日 亦都有啲想落墾丁玩（本身好鍾意玩水上活動）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者巴絲們有無啲其他好提議 推薦景點<br />\n全台灣邊到都無乜所謂<br />\n但唔鍾意行博物館之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅可以加我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Nightbluezz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FNightbluezz&d=hi8wbSk0%2F5PZXuKAsqUvlDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3ef190d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Nightbluezz</a><br />\n或者係到留言一齊討論下有咩好去處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1af85fe31f953c4f3796e67e107def55ddf8f2","tid":265932,"uid":40003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上兩次去台灣都係去台北<br />\n今次見之前hk express mega sales 有平飛買左六月十飛台中，十四號由台北翻香港<br />\n一個人飛，<br />\n有無巴絲有興趣一齊食個飯或者去下景點之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住宿都未訂<br />\n初步有構思想去高美濕地或者青境養場玩兩日 亦都有啲想落墾丁玩（本身好鍾意玩水上活動）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者巴絲們有無啲其他好提議 推薦景點<br />\n全台灣邊到都無乜所謂<br />\n但唔鍾意行博物館之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅可以加我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Nightbluezz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FNightbluezz&d=hi8wbSk0%2F5PZXuKAsqUvlDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3ef190d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://